            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "We would like to extend our heartfelt gratitude to the school and the entire team for organizing such a remarkable \"Tribute to Mahatma\" show.\nThe event was a wonderful tribute, and we truly appreciate Parina Ma'am's dedication in guiding our daughter to perform confidently and deliver the narration with poise. Her support has greatly contributed to our child's growth.\nWe also want to thank all the didis, teachers, and staff who worked tirelessly behind the scenes to make the event a success.\nYour collective efforts made this an unforgettable experience for the students and parents alike.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
