            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It was heartwarming and memorable experience to attend \"Tribute to Mahatma\". The kids performances were fabulous and directly reflected the hardwork, effort and indulgence of teachers and all concerned staff of KIS. Every child was 100% stage ready and each one was equally superb. Heartfelt gratitude and congratulations to team KIS 🙏🙏🙏",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
